OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FThe mother of a Royal Navy sailor from
OL,8,FBristol who vanished almost forty
OL,9,Fyears ago hopes "people who probably
OL,10,Fknow things... come forward" ahead of
OL,11,Fan inquest.
OL,13,FSimon Parkes was a radio operator on
OL,14,Fboard HMS Illustrious and had gone on
OL,15,Fshore in Gibraltar while on leave when
OL,16,Fhe disappeared without a trace on 12
OL,17,FDecember 1986.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
