OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FParkes, who was 18-year-old when he
OL,8,Fwas last seen, is still classed as
OL,9,F'missing' by the Royal Navy and his
OL,10,Fbody has never been found.
OL,12,FMargaret Parkes, Simon's mother, lives
OL,13,Fin Kingswood in South Gloucestershire
OL,14,Fbut has flown out to Gibraltar to help
OL,15,Fsearch for her son many times.
OL,17,FShe has said she believes "there are
OL,18,Fpeople who probably know things" and
OL,19,Fshe hopes they will come forward.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
