OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FAn inquest is now being held into the
OL,8,Ffate of Simon Parkes, something that
OL,9,FMargaret is "really pleased" is
OL,10,Fhappening, after initially having her
OL,11,Frequest for an inquest in 2006
OL,12,Frejected.
OL,14,F"All along we've wanted the truth, and
OL,15,Fwhichever way we could go to get it,
OL,16,Fand the help we've had now means the
OL,17,Finquest is happening," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
