OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FAlthough she was surprised to learn an
OL,8,Finquest has been granted, she believes
OL,9,Fit is because she believes more
OL,10,Fevidence has come to light.
OL,12,FDivers who searched a water tank in
OL,13,FGibraltar in January this year said
OL,14,Fthey had found nothing to move the
OL,15,Fcase on.
OL,17,FBut Margaret is hopeful that the
OL,18,Finquest may lead to new testimonies
OL,19,Fabout her son's fate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
