OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,F"I think the truth will be that Simon
OL,8,Fwas unlawfully killed on December 12,
OL,9,F1986 and I'm really hopeful that that
OL,10,Fwill come through", she said.
OL,12,F"The answers are there - they haven't
OL,13,Fcome out into public view yet and this
OL,14,Finquest will do that, I hope. And of
OL,15,Fcourse, it is giving publicity for
OL,16,Fanyone who really could still come
OL,17,Fforward, not just in Gibraltar, but
OL,18,Fall over the world.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
