OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,F"Ordinary people, the people of
OL,8,FGibraltar, there are people who
OL,9,Fprobably know things and they can
OL,10,Fstill come forward," she added.
OL,12,FPeople have provided new evidence "in
OL,13,Frecent years", which Margaret finds
OL,14,F"incredible".
OL,16,F"It's amazing that people come forward
OL,17,Fafter so many years - and they have
OL,18,Fdone. There's never any reason why not
OL,19,F(earlier), it's just the right time
OL,20,Ffor them - and us."
