OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FOne of her main hopes is that the
OL,8,Finquest might lead to more information
OL,9,Fabout what happened to Simon, so that
OL,10,Fhe may at last be given a proper
OL,11,Ffuneral.
OL,13,F"To find Simon is the main aim.
OL,14,FWhether we'll get there, I don't know."
OL,16,FShe added: "We're hoping that someone
OL,17,Fwill be brought to justice but that's
OL,18,Fnot the aim of this. In fact, what we
OL,19,Freally want to do is find his remains
OL,20,Fand bring him home."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
