OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,F"Obviously, the inquest is nothing to
OL,8,Fdo with how, or what or whom - why he
OL,9,Fwas killed - it's just the fact that
OL,10,Fhe was killed, that's the truth of
OL,11,Fthat", Margaret said. "Hopefully that
OL,12,Fwill lead on to maybe more evidence
OL,13,Fthat will bring in who actually killed
OL,14,Fhim."
OL,16,FSimon's mother has said she has had to
OL,17,Flearn to "get on" with her life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
