OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,F"The raw pain of your grief, over 37
OL,8,Fyears, it dissipates, but it's there.
OL,9,FWe're normal people living a normal
OL,10,Flife, but underneath it all, is (the
OL,11,Fquestion) 'where is Simon?'"
OL,13,FShe has visited Gibraltar on multiple
OL,14,Foccasions and has held a ceremony for
OL,15,FSimon, where a trees was planted on
OL,16,Fthe island in his memory.
OL,18,FShe says the people of Gibraltar are
OL,19,F"so supportive, they're absolutely
OL,20,Fwonderful."
