OL,3,CMother of Navy sailor missing since
OL,4,C1986 appeals for witnesses to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FMargaret added: "They're all behind us
OL,8,Fin wanting to know the truth."
OL,10,FWhile the news of the inquest is
OL,11,Fwelcome for Margaret, she still does
OL,12,Fnot know when it will actually take
OL,13,Fplace.
OL,15,F"But", she added, "after 37 years,
OL,16,Fthere's no rush really is there?"
